OR THEY'RE GONNA KILL ME.

215
00:13:08,711 --> 00:13:10,911
[BEEPING]
TRAINING WILL NOW BEGIN.

216
00:13:13,244 --> 00:13:16,177
AH, DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
I BET I CAN PASS THE EXAM...

217
00:13:16,211 --> 00:13:18,977
WITHOUT HAVING TO DO
ALL THIS TRAINING CRAP ANYWAY.

218
00:13:19,011 --> 00:13:21,711
I'VE ALREADY ANNIHILATED A
BOATLOAD OF DEMONS, SO I'M SET.

219
00:13:21,744 --> 00:13:23,544
OH, YEAH?
WASN'T THAT JUST DUMB LUCK?

220
00:13:23,577 --> 00:13:25,477
DUMB?
[SHOUTS]

221
00:13:25,511 --> 00:13:27,111
[GROANING]

222
00:13:27,144 --> 00:13:29,344
YOU JUST TOLD SUGURO
TO TRUST YOU.

223
00:13:29,377 --> 00:13:31,011
OR WAS I HEARING THINGS?

224
00:13:31,044 --> 00:13:33,311
SO? WHAT IF I DID?
[GASPS]

225
00:13:33,344 --> 00:13:37,144
IF YOU WANNA EARN
SOMEONE'S TRUST, YOU HAVE
TO PROVE YOURSELF TO THEM.

226
00:13:37,177 --> 00:13:40,377
AND THE WAY THINGS ARE,
YOU'VE GOT A LOT LEFT TO PROVE
TO EVERYONE.

227
00:13:40,411 --> 00:13:41,877
YEAH? LIKE WHAT?

228
00:13:41,911 --> 00:13:43,611
[SHURA]
THE FOUR-EYED CHICKEN'S
ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

229
00:13:43,644 --> 00:13:45,077
[YUKIO]
SHURA.

230
00:13:45,111 --> 00:13:47,244
[RIN]
WHAT'S WITH THAT OUTFIT?

231
00:13:47,277 --> 00:13:48,977
IT'S CALLED ECO FRIENDLY.

232
00:13:49,011 --> 00:13:52,211
[THINKING]
ECO FRIENDLY? YOU JUST
SHOWED UP IN YOUR PAJAMAS.

233
00:13:52,244 --> 00:13:56,444
SINCE YOU'RE THE SPAWN OF SATAN
AND ALL, YOU'RE KINDA LIKE
A DEMONIC THOROUGHBRED.

234
00:13:56,477 --> 00:14:00,377
THE ONLY REASON YOU MANAGED
TO GET BY TILL NOW IS 'CAUSE OF
ALL THAT UNTAPPED POTENTIAL.

235
00:14:00,411 --> 00:14:03,177
THAT'S IT.
AND EVEN WITH
ALL THAT POTENTIAL,

236
00:14:03,211 --> 00:14:06,277
YOU STILL HAVE TO FIGURE OUT
HOW TO CONTROL THOSE POWERS.

237
00:14:06,311 --> 00:14:10,011
TILL THEN, YOU GOT NO CHANCE
OF BECOMING AN EXORCIST,
NEVER MIND A PALADIN.

238
00:14:10,044 --> 00:14:12,877
WELL, THEN WHAT AM I
SUPPOSED TO DO?

239
00:14:12,911 --> 00:14:15,077
TRAIN YOUR ASS OFF,
NATCH.

240
00:14:15,111 --> 00:14:17,477
- HERE.
- [GASPS]
A CANDLE?

241
00:14:17,511 --> 00:14:22,044
DUH. OKAY, FIRST, LINE UP
THREE OF THOSE CANDLES
SIDE BY SIDE,

242
00:14:22,077 --> 00:14:24,377
AND TRY TO LIGHT THE ONES
ON EACH END
AT THE SAME TIME.

243
00:14:24,411 --> 00:14:25,777
GOT IT.

244
00:14:28,111 --> 00:14:30,844
[GRUNTING]

245
00:14:34,377 --> 00:14:38,644
[GASPS]
LIGHT THEM, NOT ENGULF THEM
IN YOUR UNGODLY HELL FIRE.

246
00:14:38,677 --> 00:14:39,877
YEAH, I'LL TRY IT AGAIN.

247
00:14:41,177 --> 00:14:42,111
REALLY?

248
00:14:42,144 --> 00:14:44,844
UH, THAT'S THE MIDDLE ONE,
DUMBASS.

249
00:14:45,944 --> 00:14:48,011
I SAID LIGHT 'EM
AT THE SAME TIME.

250
00:14:48,044 --> 00:14:50,077
- [SHOUTING]
- YOU'RE SO SLOPPY,

251
00:14:50,111 --> 00:14:51,911
SLOPPY DOESN'T EVEN BEGIN
TO DESCRIBE YOU.

252
00:14:51,944 --> 00:14:53,444
BUT THIS IS REALLY HARD.

253
00:14:53,477 --> 00:14:56,844
BOO-FRICKIN'-HOO.
YOU'RE DOING THREE SETS A DAY
FOR AN HOUR EACH.

254
00:14:56,877 --> 00:15:00,344
I WANT YOU TO KEEP AT IT
TILL YOU CAN DO IT EVEN WHILE
YOU'RE PICKING YOUR NOSE.

255
00:15:00,377 --> 00:15:02,777
HUH?
THAT'S MY TRAINING?

256
00:15:02,811 --> 00:15:04,544
WH-WHAT ABOUT MY SWORD?

257
00:15:04,577 --> 00:15:06,511
[SIGHS]
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA...

258
00:15:06,544 --> 00:15:09,544
WHY YOU LOST CONTROL OF YOURSELF
DURING YOUR FIGHT WITH AMAIMON?

259
00:15:09,577 --> 00:15:12,711
UH-UH.
NOT A CLUE.

260
00:15:12,744 --> 00:15:14,844
YOU LOST IT 'CAUSE YOU CHICKENED
OUT, THAT'S WHY.

261
00:15:14,877 --> 00:15:17,711
IT'S WHY YOUR FLAMES
CONSUME YOU.

262
00:15:17,744 --> 00:15:20,177
GET USED TO YOUR FLAMES,
BUILD UP YOUR CONFIDENCE.

263
00:15:20,211 --> 00:15:22,611
THEN WE CAN TALK
ABOUT THE KOMA SWORD.

264
00:15:22,644 --> 00:15:26,311
[THINKING]
IT PISSES ME OFF,
BUT SHE'S RIGHT, DAMN IT.

265
00:15:26,344 --> 00:15:28,311
OKAY. I GOT THIS.

266
00:15:28,344 --> 00:15:29,944
[GASPS, GROANS]

267
00:15:29,977 --> 00:15:32,711
I WONDER IF THE KID'S
EVER GONNA GET IT.

268
00:15:32,744 --> 00:15:34,011
[RIN GRUNTING]
HUH?

269
00:15:34,044 --> 00:15:36,744
YOU LOOK ALL GLOOMY
AS USUAL.

270
00:15:36,777 --> 00:15:40,044
YOU KNOW, YOU KEEP HANGING ON
TO THAT STRESS,
YOU'RE GONNA GET AN ULCER.

271
00:15:40,077 --> 00:15:41,711
AND WHOSE FAULT WOULD THAT BE?

272
00:15:41,744 --> 00:15:44,344
I GOT AN IDEA,
MR. FOUR-EYED CHICKEN.

273
00:15:44,377 --> 00:15:46,711
HOW ABOUT WE TAKE THE EDGE OFF
EXORCIST STYLE?

274
00:15:46,744 --> 00:15:49,244
- PASS.
- HOLY CRAP, THAT WAS FAST.

275
00:15:49,277 --> 00:15:51,077
YOU'RE SO ANTISOCIAL.

276
00:15:51,111 --> 00:15:55,677
REMEMBER THE DAYS
WE USED TO BET EACH OTHER LUNCH
ON THESE MATCHES?

277
00:15:55,711 --> 00:15:58,644
WHOO-HOO!
SIXTEEN WINS IN A ROW
FOR ME!

278
00:15:58,677 --> 00:16:00,177
[LAUGHING]
[GROANS]

279
00:16:00,211 --> 00:16:04,377
HEY, SHURA, IT'S NOT COOL
TO GO ALL OUT
AGAINST A MIDDLE SCHOOLER.

280
00:16:04,411 --> 00:16:09,277
RELAX. I WAS JUST SHOWING HIM
HOW BRUTAL THE COMPETITION
CAN BE IN THE REAL WORLD.

281
00:16:09,311 --> 00:16:13,344
YO, CHICKEN, YOU LOST TODAY,
SO YOU'RE BUYING ME LUNCH
TOMORROW.

282
00:16:13,377 --> 00:16:17,077
OKAY, WHATEVER.
JUST STOP CALLING ME
CHICKEN ALREADY.

283
00:16:17,111 --> 00:16:18,977
[LAUGHS]

284
00:16:19,011 --> 00:16:22,411
YOU KNOW, YUKIO,
YOU'RE TOTALLY GETTING
PLAYED BY HER.

285
00:16:22,444 --> 00:16:24,211
- BULLSHIT.
- [GASPS]

286
00:16:24,244 --> 00:16:27,677
DID YOU JUST SAY "BULLSHIT"?
UNBELIEVABLE.

287
00:16:27,711 --> 00:16:29,977
I REALLY DON'T LIKE THAT GIRL
ONE BIT.

288
00:16:30,011 --> 00:16:33,277
SHE'S GOT ALL THAT TALENT,
BUT SHE'S ALWAYS SLACKING OFF.

289
00:16:33,311 --> 00:16:36,677
SHE MAKES ME FEEL LIKE AN IDIOT
FOR STUDYING SO HARD.

290
00:16:36,711 --> 00:16:39,477
THERE'S TWO SIDES
TO EVERY STORY, SON.

291
00:16:39,511 --> 00:16:43,311
EVEN THOUGH SHE DOESN'T ACT
LIKE IT, SHE WORKS HER BUTT OFF
JUST LIKE YOU.

292
00:16:46,377 --> 00:16:48,644
OKAY, I'M IN.
HOWEVER,

293
00:16:48,677 --> 00:16:52,977
IF I WIN, YOU HAVE TO STOP
CALLING ME "FOUR-EYED CHICKEN,"
YOU GOT THAT?

294
00:16:53,011 --> 00:16:56,511
HMM. SURE.
SAME RULES AS BEFORE.
WE ROCK INFINITY MODE,

295
00:16:56,544 --> 00:16:59,777
AND THE FIRST ONE
WHO LOSES THEIR CONCENTRATION
LOSES THE BET.

296
00:16:59,811 --> 00:17:01,977
SOUND GOOD?
I CAN LIVE WITH THAT.

297
00:17:02,011 --> 00:17:05,311
[BEEPING]
YOU HAVE SELECTED
SPECIAL INFINITY MODE.

298
00:17:05,344 --> 00:17:07,011
TRAINING WILL NOW BEGIN.

299
00:17:10,877 --> 00:17:14,144
HOLY CRAP!
THOSE THINGS
ARE GOING SO FAST,

300
00:17:14,177 --> 00:17:16,777
BUT THEY'RE SMASHING
EVERY ONE OF 'EM
LIKE IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

301
00:17:16,811 --> 00:17:18,677
THOSE GUYS ARE MACHINES.

302
00:17:18,711 --> 00:17:22,111
WHAT THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?
GO FOCUS ON YOUR CANDLES, KID.

303
00:17:22,144 --> 00:17:24,777
ACTUALLY, SHURA,
YOU SHOULD BE THE ONE FOCUSING.

304
00:17:24,811 --> 00:17:27,277
DON'T GIVE ME YOUR LIP, CHICKEN.

305
00:17:27,311 --> 00:17:28,977
KEEP SHOOTING.

306
00:17:29,011 --> 00:17:31,511
HE'S BEHIND THE PILLAR
ON THE SOUTH SIDE
OF THE TRAINING ROOM.

307
00:17:31,544 --> 00:17:35,011
EVEN THOUGH HE'S KEEPING HIMSELF
HIDDEN, YOU CAN SEE HIM, YEAH?

308
00:17:35,044 --> 00:17:37,944
- IS HE WORKING
FOR THE VATICAN?
- UH-HUH.

309
00:17:37,977 --> 00:17:41,077
BUT RIN'S NOT THE ONLY ONE
HE'S KEEPING AN EYE ON.

310
00:17:41,111 --> 00:17:43,811
- HE'S WATCHING YOU.
- WHY WOULD THE GRIGORI
DO THAT?

311
00:17:43,844 --> 00:17:47,811
THEY ORDERED ME TO WATCH RIN.
THEY TRUST ME.

312
00:17:47,844 --> 00:17:50,177
[SHURA]
BUT YOU'RE THE SON OF SATAN TOO.

313
00:17:50,211 --> 00:17:53,377
TO THE VATICAN, YOU'RE AS MUCH
OF A THREAT TO THEM
AS YOUR BROTHER.

314
00:17:53,411 --> 00:17:55,144
I'M NOTHING LIKE MY BROTHER.

315
00:17:55,177 --> 00:17:57,477
IN CASE YOU HADN'T NOTICED,
I DON'T HAVE HIS POWERS.

316
00:17:57,511 --> 00:18:00,977
IF YOU REALLY BELIEVE THAT,
HOW COME YOU GET YOURSELF
CHECKED OUT EVERY DAY?

317
00:18:01,011 --> 00:18:03,144
IT'S 'CAUSE YOU'RE AFRAID,
THAT'S WHY.

318
00:18:03,177 --> 00:18:07,311
YOU THINK THE DAY IS GONNA COME
WHEN YOU'LL FIND YOURSELF WITH
THE SAME DEMONIC POWER AS RIN.

319
00:18:07,344 --> 00:18:10,044
- THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
- OR MAYBE IT'S
THE OTHER WAY AROUND.

320
00:18:10,077 --> 00:18:12,544
MAYBE YOU WANNA HAVE THAT POWER
ALL FOR YOURSELF.

321
00:18:12,577 --> 00:18:16,477
NICE TRY, BUT YOU CAN'T
DISTRACT ME BY MESSING
WITH MY HEAD LIKE THAT.

322
00:18:16,511 --> 00:18:19,111
I HOPE THAT'S TRUE.
WATCH OUT.

323
00:18:19,144 --> 00:18:22,344
YOU'RE THE TYPE WHO GETS
POSSESSED BY DEMONS EASY.
I CAN TELL.

324
00:18:22,377 --> 00:18:24,111
WHAT?

325
00:18:24,144 --> 00:18:26,677
[THINKING]
IS THAT HOW GOOD
A PRO'S SUPPOSED TO BE?

326
00:18:26,711 --> 00:18:31,277
MAN, IT TOOK EVERYTHING I HAD
JUST TO HIT A COUPLE OF THEM
IN BEGINNER MODE.

327
00:18:31,311 --> 00:18:32,844
[GRUNTS]
SHIT!

328
00:18:33,811 --> 00:18:35,777
- WHAT THE HELL?
- WHAT'S GOING ON?

329
00:18:35,811 --> 00:18:37,477
[STAMMERING]

330
00:18:37,511 --> 00:18:39,644
UH--

331
00:18:39,677 --> 00:18:41,511
WHY DID YOU DO THIS
TO US, RIN?

332
00:18:41,544 --> 00:18:44,911
HUH? SORRY. MY BAD.

333
00:18:44,944 --> 00:18:47,011
HOLD UP THOUGH.
YOUR CLOTHES BURNED OFF,

334
00:18:47,044 --> 00:18:49,044
BUT NOT YOUR UNDERWEAR OR SKIN.

335
00:18:49,077 --> 00:18:52,277
YOU SEE? THAT PROVES
I CAN CONTROL MY POWER.

336
00:18:52,311 --> 00:18:54,277
THE HELL YOU CAN.

337
00:18:54,311 --> 00:18:56,477
YEAH, I GUESS YOU'RE RIGHT.
[GIGGLES]

338
00:18:56,511 --> 00:18:57,944
I'LL GET
THE HOLY WATER.

339
00:18:57,977 --> 00:18:59,444
THANKS.
THAT'D BE GREAT.

340
00:19:02,811 --> 00:19:05,344
[SUGURO]
FOR BY HIM,
ALL THINGS WERE CREATED.

341
00:19:05,377 --> 00:19:08,811
THINGS IN HEAVEN
AND ON EARTH--
STILL STUDYING?

342
00:19:08,844 --> 00:19:10,511
SORRY ABOUT THAT, MAN.
DIDN'T MEAN TO WAKE YOU.

343
00:19:10,544 --> 00:19:12,544
I JUST GOT UP
TO USE THE RESTROOM.

344
00:19:12,577 --> 00:19:16,411
YOU SHOULD TRY TO GET
SOME SLEEP, THOUGH,
OR YOU'LL BURN YOURSELF OUT.

345
00:19:16,444 --> 00:19:18,444
BUT I DON'T WANNA LOSE.

346
00:19:18,477 --> 00:19:20,511
[GASPS]
TO WHOM? KAMIKI?

347
00:19:20,544 --> 00:19:23,777
NO, YOU DUMMY.
I MEAN TO OKUMURA.

348
00:19:23,811 --> 00:19:26,177
YOU'RE WAY AHEAD OF HIM.
YOU'RE THE TOP STUDENT...

349
00:19:26,211 --> 00:19:28,977
IN PHARMACOLOGY
<i>AND</i> SCRIPTURE RECITATION.

350
00:19:29,011 --> 00:19:33,144
YEAH, BUT STRAIGHT A'S
AREN'T GONNA HELP ANYONE
IN REAL-WORLD COMBAT.

351
00:19:33,177 --> 00:19:35,711
[SIGHS]
THAT HIT HOME
AFTER OUR CAMPING TRIP.

352
00:19:35,744 --> 00:19:38,077
[SIGHS]
BON--

353
00:19:38,111 --> 00:19:43,177
I PROMISE I'M GONNA BECOME
A FULL-FLEDGED EXORCIST
AS SOON AS I CAN.

354
00:19:43,211 --> 00:19:48,144
OTHERWISE I WON'T BE ABLE
TO HOLD MY HEAD UP
TO YOUR MOM AND DAD.

355
00:19:48,177 --> 00:19:50,144
[MIWA]
RIGHT.

356
00:19:51,477 --> 00:19:54,144
BON IS SO STRONG.

357
00:19:54,177 --> 00:19:59,044
EVEN AFTER WHAT WE SAW,
HE STILL THINKS OKUMURA
IS HIS RIVAL,

358
00:19:59,077 --> 00:20:02,311
WHILE I CAN'T EVEN BE
IN THE SAME ROOM AS HE IS.

359
00:20:04,044 --> 00:20:06,711
[MALE VOICE]
ARE YOU AFRAID?
[GASPS]

360
00:20:08,611 --> 00:20:11,077
YOU'LL END UP
LOSING THEM AGAIN--

361
00:20:11,111 --> 00:20:14,477
YOUR LOVED ONES;
THOSE DEAR TO YOU.

362
00:20:14,511 --> 00:20:18,177
NOW THEN,
ACCEPT ME.

363
00:20:18,211 --> 00:20:20,444
WHO ARE YOU?

364
00:20:23,711 --> 00:20:26,011
ACCEPT THIS FEAR.

365
00:20:26,044 --> 00:20:27,244
[GASPS]

366
00:20:30,183 --> 00:20:31,583
[RIN GRUNTING]

367
00:20:31,617 --> 00:20:34,904
OH, COME ON, MAN!
WHY CAN'T I MAKE IT DO
WHAT I WANT IT TO?

368
00:20:34,937 --> 00:20:37,337
OH, I GUESS I DON'T HAVE
THE TALENT FOR IT.

369
00:20:37,370 --> 00:20:39,837
[FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING]
UH, WHO'S THERE?

370
00:20:39,870 --> 00:20:43,537
IT'S ME WONDERING WHY
YOU'RE SITTING THERE
TALKING TO YOURSELF.

371
00:20:43,570 --> 00:20:44,904
I WASN'T.

372
00:20:44,937 --> 00:20:47,704
ANYWAY, WHY ARE YOU SNEAKING
AROUND HERE THIS EARLY
IN THE MORNING?

373
00:20:47,737 --> 00:20:50,570
I'M NOT SNEAKING.
I JUST FORGOT
MY PENCIL CASE.

374
00:20:50,604 --> 00:20:51,970
UH-- OH.

375
00:20:52,004 --> 00:20:54,970
WHAT KIND OF TRAINING
IS THAT SUPPOSED TO BE?

376
00:20:55,004 --> 00:20:58,037
OH. I HAVE TO LIGHT THE CANDLES
ON THE ENDS,

377
00:20:58,070 --> 00:21:01,470
NOT THE ONE IN THE MIDDLE,
BUT IT'S NOT WORKING OUT
SO HOT FOR ME.

378
00:21:01,504 --> 00:21:05,070
THAT REMINDS ME.
REMEMBER WHEN PAKO
GOT ATTACKED BY THAT GHOUL?

379
00:21:05,104 --> 00:21:07,737
YEAH.
DURING THAT BOOT CAMP THING.

380
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:11,937
THAT DAY MY FAMILIARS
WOULDN'T OBEY ME
BECAUSE I WAS SCARED.

381
00:21:11,970 --> 00:21:14,804
I LOST MY CONFIDENCE.
AND I LOST CONTROL.

382
00:21:14,837 --> 00:21:16,670
YOUR FLAMES WORK THE SAME WAY.

383
00:21:16,704 --> 00:21:19,704
DON'T BE AFRAID.
BE CONFIDENT, AND I'M SURE
THEY'LL OBEY YOU.

384
00:21:19,737 --> 00:21:21,804
THAT MAKES SENSE.

385
00:21:21,837 --> 00:21:23,270
HEY, WHY'D YOU DO THAT?

386
00:21:23,304 --> 00:21:25,237
WHAT?
YOU GAVE ME GOOD ADVICE.

387
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:27,437
WHY'D YOU GO OUT OF YOUR WAY
TO TELL ME ALL THAT STUFF?

388
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:30,537
I MEAN, AREN'T YOU SCARED OF ME
LIKE EVERYONE ELSE?

389
00:21:30,570 --> 00:21:33,270
NOT REALLY.
I GUESS YOU
DIDN'T KNOW THIS,

390
00:21:33,304 --> 00:21:35,504
BUT ACTUALLY
IT'S NOT THAT UNUSUAL...

391
00:21:35,537 --> 00:21:38,170
FOR DEMONS AND HUMANS
TO HAVE BLOOD TIES
WITH EACH OTHER.

392
00:21:38,204 --> 00:21:40,270
AND FOR EXORCISTS,
IT'S PRETTY COMMON.

393
00:21:40,304 --> 00:21:42,304
[GASPS]
NO WAY.
YOU'RE KIDDING.

394
00:21:42,337 --> 00:21:44,704
EVERYONE KNOWS THAT.
AND NOW THAT YOU KNOW,

395
00:21:44,737 --> 00:21:48,237
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE ALL MOPEY
AND STRESS OUT ABOUT
YOUR BLOODLINE ANYMORE.

396
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:52,770
IF PEOPLE WANNA MAKE
A BIG DEAL OUT OF IT,
THEN YOU CAN... TELL 'EM--

397
00:21:54,804 --> 00:21:56,104
THANKS, POLKA BROW!

398
00:21:56,137 --> 00:21:58,737
HUH?
YOU'RE A PRETTY RAD PERSON
AFTER ALL.

399
00:21:58,770 --> 00:21:59,970
YOU CALLED ME POLKA BROW?

400
00:22:00,004 --> 00:22:01,537
DON'T YOU GIVE ME
WEIRD NICKNAMES.

401
00:22:01,570 --> 00:22:04,237
I HAVE A PROPER NAME.
IT'S IZUMO KAMIKI, GOT THAT?

402
00:22:04,270 --> 00:22:06,437
I REALLY APPRECIATE IT, IZUMO.

403
00:22:06,470 --> 00:22:09,004
THANKS TO YOU,
I THINK I CAN DO THIS.

404
00:22:09,037 --> 00:22:10,704
[HUFFS]

405
00:22:10,737 --> 00:22:13,904
WELL, IT'S NOT LIKE I CAME HERE
WANTING TO GIVE YOU A PEP TALK.

406
00:22:13,937 --> 00:22:16,237
[WIND BLOWING]

407
00:22:16,270 --> 00:22:18,437
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

408
00:22:18,470 --> 00:22:21,104
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT IT'S COMING.

409
00:22:21,137 --> 00:22:23,137
[GRUNTS]
SHOW YOURSELF!

410
00:22:25,404 --> 00:22:27,604
[GASPS]

411
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:42,704
♪ [WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE]

412
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:05,770
[MIWA]
IT'S OKUMURA.
HE JUST CAME AFTER ME.

413
00:24:05,804 --> 00:24:09,570
[SUGURO] IF YOU EVER HURT
ANY OF MY FRIENDS,
I SWORE I'D KILL YOU.

414
00:24:09,604 --> 00:24:12,704
[YUKIO] CONTROL YOURSELF.
IF YOU GO ON ANOTHER RAMPAGE,
THEY'RE GO--

